  "plainText": "Don't Starve\nTogether\nHoney Nuggets\nNormal\nPig Fiesta\nFood Info\n37.5\n20\n5\nMeat\nObject Info\n15 Days\nCan be Burned\n40\nSource\n: ( ×5)\nCooking Info\nx1 x1 x2\n40 sec\n2\nMiscellaneous\n\"honeynuggets\"\n“Taste like chicken, but I don't think it is.”\n–Wilson\n“Honey-covered morsels that have met my friend, fire.”\n–Willow\n“Small meats with sweet still is good meat.”\n–Wolfgang\n“Meat cut into tiny pieces. Just like my heart.”\n–Wendy\n“PLEASE INSERT INTO MOUTH”\n–WX-78\n“Bite-sized sweetened meat!”\n–Wickerbottom\n“One of my favourite meals!”\n–Woodie\n“These look childish, but they're delicious.”\n–Maxwell\n“Tiny morsels of sweet protein. Excellent for my digestion.”\n–Wagstaff\n“A meaty, nuggety feast!”\n–Wigfrid\n“We wish they were shaped like dinosaurs.”\n–Webber\n“I'll just be lying here, shoving these into my mouth.”\n–Walani\n“Junk food is my guilty pleasure. Shh!”\n–Warly\n“Golden nuggets!”\n–Woodlegs\n“'TIS TINY NUM NUMS”\n–Wilba\n“Buzz Juice and Twirly Tails”\n–Wormwood\n“Tiny bits of sweet meat I can launch through the air.”\n–Wheeler\n“Not bad!”\n–Winona\n“I guess they do look kind of good.”\n–Wortox\n“Wasting honey!”\n–Wurt\n“I loved these when I was little.”\n–Walter\n“The dipping sauce is my favorite part.”\n–Wanda\nHoney Nuggets is a Meat Food item cooked in the Crock Pot by combining 1 Honey and any Meats. However, adding more than 1.5 unit of Meats will result in Honey Ham instead. It takes 40 seconds to cook.\nAdding more than 1 Monster Meat will result in Monster Lasagna, adding 1 Twig will result in Kabobs, but adding any other Inedibles will result in Wet Goop.\nPrerequisites[edit | edit source]\nRequires:\nRequires:\nExcludes:\nRecipe[edit | edit source]\nExamples[edit | edit source]\n×2\nA recipe for Honey Nuggets that produces positive stats from mostly harmful ingredients\n×2\n×2\n×3\n×2\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nDuring the Pig Fiesta event in the Hamlet DLC, Honey Nuggets take on a more festive appearance.\nWilson's quote can be a reference to the fact that Honey Nuggets don't have any chicken inside, because chickens don't exist in-game anymore.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nOriginal HD icon from Bonus Materials from CD Don't Starve.\nIcon used as emoji for Official Klei Discord.\nBy TypeBy Crock Pot Value\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Type)\nVeggie\nSeeds\nMeat\nGoodies\nGeneric\nHorrible\nRoughage\nElementals\nBurnt\nRaw\nGears\nGold Dust\nBerry\nWood\nNitre\nLunar Shards\nView or edit this template\nFood and Edible Items (by Food Value)\nMeats\nFishes\nVegetables\nFruits\nMonster Food\nEggs\nDairy\nSweetener\nFrozen\nInedibles\nMagic\nFat\nSeed\nJellyfish\nBone\nFilter\nAntihistamine\nDecoration\nBug\nNo Value Food",
